OL,3,CGold's out, wind's in: turbines
OL,4,Cplanned for South Scotland mine site
OL,6,FRenewco Power, a Glasgow-based
OL,7,Frenewable energy developer, wants to
OL,8,Fbuild 21 wind turbines that it claims
OL,9,Fcould power around 176,708 homes on
OL,10,Fthe rolling hills of southern Scotland.
OL,12,FIt wants to turn the area north of the
OL,13,Fvillage of Leadhills in South
OL,14,FLanarkshire, on the Dumfries and
OL,15,FGalloway border, into Ravengill Energy
OL,16,FPark. The plans also include a battery
OL,17,Fenergy storage system.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
