CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1784913524
OL,3,CGold's out, wind's in: turbines
OL,4,Cplanned for South Scotland mine site
OL,6,FIt is believed part of the suggested
OL,7,Fsite was mined for lead and gold from
OL,8,Fthe 16th to 20th Century, as disused
OL,9,Fmines and equipment has been seen in
OL,10,Fthe area.
OL,12,FRenewco Power claims it would play a
OL,13,Fsignificant role in both Scotland and
OL,14,Fthe wider UK meeting their emissions
OL,15,Freduction and net zero commitments.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
