CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1784913524
OL,3,CGold's out, wind's in: turbines
OL,4,Cplanned for South Scotland mine site
OL,6,FThe company writes, "Significant
OL,7,Fadditional renewable energy capacity,
OL,8,Fover and above what is produced today,
OL,9,Fwill be needed to facilitate the
OL,10,Fdecarbonisation of transport and
OL,11,Fheating as Scotland transitions to net
OL,12,Fzero."
OL,14,FThe developer argues the site is right
OL,15,Ffor this development because:
OL,17,FThey also claim it can be done without
OL,18,F"significant direct effects" on
OL,19,Fdesignated nature conservation areas.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
