FL,328,320,120,260,000,100
PN,32704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1784913524
OL,3,CGold's out, wind's in: turbines
OL,4,Cplanned for South Scotland mine site
OL,6,FLocal campaigners disagree though.
OL,7,FPrevious applications for other wind
OL,8,Ffarms in the area have already met
OL,9,Fresistance from local people.
OL,11,FSome in the Ravengill Action Group
OL,12,Fargue it will "destroy" the "beautiful
OL,13,Flandscape" of such a large area of
OL,14,Fhills.
OL,16,FThey also feel this area has now more
OL,17,Fthan done its bit for providing wind
OL,18,Fenergy and question if the electricity
OL,19,Fwill stay in Scotland or actually be
OL,20,Fused south of the border.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/6
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
