CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F327A1784913524
OL,3,CGold's out, wind's in: turbines
OL,4,Cplanned for South Scotland mine site
OL,6,FAn application for consent has been
OL,7,Fsubmitted to the Scottish Government,
OL,8,Fincluding an Environmental Impact
OL,9,FAssessment Report (EIAR) and report on
OL,10,Fthe consultation with the local
OL,11,Fcommunity so far.
OL,13,FIf approved, Renewco Power plans for
OL,14,Fthe site to be in operation for 40
OL,15,Fyears from 2036.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/6
